 enter the store locator from any possible entrance\\r\\nTHEN the store locator must display a pre-populated list with stores within a 100km radius from where the users location\\r\\n\\r\\nh5. Scenario 2: geo location button is highlighted \\r\\nGIVEN scenario 1\\r\\nTHEN the geo location button is highlighted as per design attached\\r\\n\",\"customfield_21380\":null,\"customfield_10252\":null,\"customfield_21379\":null,\"summary\":\"[OLIN-4676][iOS] User with location sharing enabled\",\"customfield_21378\":null,\"customfield_21377\":null,\"customfield_21376\":null,\"customfield_21375\":null,\"customfield_11170\":null,\"customfield_15770\":null,\"customfield_21374\":null,\"customfield_21770\":null,\"customfield_21373\":null,\"customfield_21372\":null,\"customfield_21371\":null,\"customfield_11571\":\"2018-06-01T13:39:03.530+0200\",\"customfield_21370\":null,\"customfield_11572\":null,\"duedate\":null}},{\"expand\":\"operations,versionedRepresentations,editmeta,changelog,renderedFields\",\"id\":\"669446\",\"self\":\"https://jira.hm.com/rest/api/2/issue/669446\",\"key\":\"HMCOM-47515\",\"fields\":{\"customfield_16970\":\"2|i0jkuv:\",\"customfield_22571\":null,\"customfield_10076\":null,\"customfield_10230\":null,\"fixVersions\":[{\"self\":\"https://jira.hm.com/rest/api/2/version/44653\",\"id\":\"44653\",\"description\":\"Joshua/START 2018:JUN - patch\",\"name\":\"Joshua/START 2018:JUN\",\"archived\":false,\"released\":false,\"releaseDate\":\"2018-06-19\"}],\"customfield_10111\":null,\"customfield_10232\":null,\"resolution\":null,\"customfield_10112\":\"h3. Preconditions\\r\\nWhat is needed to perform the test?\\r\\n\\r\\nh4. Environments\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nh4. Test data\\r\\nMarket:\\r\\nCustomer:\\r\\n\\r\\nh4. Technical notes/information\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n \",\"customfield_10871\":null,\"customfield_10872\":null,\"lastViewed\":\"2018-06-12T09:10:55.629+0200\",\"customfield_10060\":null,\"customfield_11270\":\"9223372036854775807\",\"customfield_19670\":null,\"customfi