ogress\":{\"progress\":0,\"total\":0},\"customfield_13279\":null,\"progress\":{\"progress\":0,\"total\":0},\"votes\":{\"self\":\"https://jira.hm.com/rest/api/2/issue/HMCOM-47515/votes\",\"votes\":0,\"hasVoted\":false},\"customfield_17072\":null,\"customfield_17071\":null,\"customfield_17070\":null,\"issuetype\":{\"self\":\"https://jira.hm.com/rest/api/2/issuetype/13\",\"id\":\"13\",\"description\":\"Created by JIRA Software - do not edit or delete. Issue type for a user story.\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://jira.hm.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=34963&avatarType=issuetype\",\"name\":\"Story\",\"subtask\":false,\"avatarId\":34963},\"customfield_12170\":null,\"customfield_21682\":null,\"customfield_21681\":null,\"customfield_10270\":\"9223372036854775807\",\"customfield_21680\":null,\"timespent\":null,\"customfield_10030\":null,\"customfield_10031\":null,\"project\":{\"self\":\"https://jira.hm.com/rest/api/2/project/10442\",\"id\":\"10442\",\"key\":\"HMCOM\",\"name\":\"HM.com - Site\",\"avatarUrls\":{\"48x48\":\"https://jira.hm.com/secure/projectavatar?pid=10442&avatarId=10860\",\"24x24\":\"https://jira.hm.com/secure/projectavatar?size=small&pid=10442&avatarId=10860\",\"16x16\":\"https://jira.hm.com/secure/projectavatar?size=xsmall&pid=10442&avatarId=10860\",\"32x32\":\"https://jira.hm.com/secure/projectavatar?size=medium&pid=10442&avatarId=10860\"},\"projectCategory\":{\"self\":\"https://jira.hm.com/rest/api/2/projectCategory/10806\",\"id\":\"10806\",\"description\":\"\",\"name\":\"Sales Online & Marketing - Sales Online\"}},\"customfield_12970\":\"HMCOM-47478\",\"customfield_14871\":null,\"customfield_10034\":null,\"aggregatetimespent\":null,\"resolutiondate\":null,\"workratio\":-1,\"customfield_21679\":null,\"customfield_21678\":null,\"customfield_21677\":null,\"customfield_21676\":null,\"customfield_15271\":null,\"customfield_21675\":null,\"customfield_21674\":null,\"watches\":{\"self\":\"https://jira.hm.com/rest/api/2/issue/HMCOM-47515/watchers\",\"watchCount\":3,\"isWatching\":true},\"customfield_21673\":null,\"customfield_11070\":null,\"customfield_15270\":null,\"customfield_21672\":null,\"customfield_11071\":{\"self\":\"https://jira.hm.com/rest/api/2/customFieldOption/14058\",\"value\":\"Mobile\",\"id\":\"14058\"},\"customfield_21671\":null,\"customfield_11072\":null,\"customfield_13370\":null,\"customfield_21670\":null,\"customfield_21273\":null,\"created\":\"2018-04-09T15:03:50.000+0200\",\"customfield_21272\":null,\"customfield_13771\":{\"self\":\"https://jira.hm.com/rest/api/2/customFieldOption/16140\",\"value\":\"Undefined\",\"id\":\"16140\"},\"customfield_21271\":null,\"customfield_11471\":null,\"customfield_21270\":null,\"customfield_13773\":null,\"updated\":\"2018-06-07T09:20:08.000+0200\",\"customfield_21388\":null,\"customfield_10090\":[{\"self\":\"https://jira.hm.com/rest/api/2/customFieldOption/10390\",\"value\":\"Impediment\",\"id\":\"10390\"}],\"customfield_21387\":null,\"customfield_10091\":null,\"customfield_21386\":null,\"customfield_20570\":null,\"customfield_21385\":null,\"customfield_10093\":1.0,\"customfield_16870\":\"0|hzzyfl:\",\"customfield_21384\":null,\"customfield_21383\":null,\"customfield_10370\":null,\"customfield_21382\":null,\"timeoriginalestimate\":null,\"customfield_21381\":null,\"description\":\"h3. User story\\r\\n\\r\\n*AS A* tablet user on \\\"Customer Service – Contact\\r\\n *I WANT TO* have the relevant information presented to me when I click the privacy notice\\r\\n *SO THAT* I easily can grasp the important content\\r\\nh4. Background/Business needs\\r\\n\\r\\nTo be compliant with GDPR, H&M needs to add a lot of information to be privacy notice, and due to this additional information, the privacy notice as whole will become a much longer text. One way to make this information easier to grasp for the user is to divide it into chapters, and only display the chapter that is relevant to the part of hm.com the user are on when clicking on the privacy policy link.\\r\\nh4. Dependencies\\r\\n\\r\\nContent mgmt team\\r\\nh4. Notes/Detailed Requirement\\r\\n - On the domain \\\"Customer Service – Contact\\\" we must display the chapter regarding customer service in the privacy notice.\\r\\n - Update with the relevant URL in the controller for this page\\r\\n - the content in the overlays are entered by the CMM team manually in the Hybris CMS Cockpit.\\r\\n - \\r\\n -- The new content to be added (as pet the PPT UX), and for which translations are to be ordered:\\r\\nMaster value:\\r\\n{code:java}\\r\\nFor questions regarding your personal data, and instructions on how to access or delete your stored information, please visit our <a href=\\\"privacy_policy\\\" class=\\\"information\\\" target=\\\"overlay\\\">Privacy Notice</a>.\\r\\n{code}\\r\\nGerman translation:\\r\\n{code:java}\\r\\nBei Fragen zu personenbezogenen Daten und Hinweisen, wie Sie die über Sie gespeicherten Daten einsehen oder löschen können, lesen Sie in unserer <a href=\\\"privacy_policy\\\" class=\\\"information\\\" target=\\\"overlay\\\">Datenschutzerklärung</a> nach.\\r\\n{code}\\r\\n*AND*\\r\\n\\r\\nMaster value:\\r\\n{code:java}\\r\\nWhen you contact Customer Service we will process your personal data in accordance with our <a href=\\\"privacy_policy_customer_service\\\" class=\\\"information\\\" target=\\\"overlay\\\">Privacy Notice</a>.\\r\\n{code}\\r\\nGerman translation:\\r\\n{code:java}\\r\\nWenn Sie den Kundenservice kontaktieren, werden Ihre personenbezogenen Daten gemäß unserer <a href=\\\"privacy_policy_customer_service\\\" class=\\\"information\\\" target=\\\"overlay\\\">Datenschutzerklärung</a> verarbeitet.{code}\\r\\n\\r\\nh4. URL´s\\r\\n # Here are the new URL´s\\r\\n||No.||Page name||Page URL||\\r\\n|1|Privacy notice (lightbox) - H&M account|/privacy_notice_account|\\r\\n|2|Privacy notice (lightbox) - H&M Club|/privacy_notice_club|\\r\\n|3|Privacy notice (lightbox) – Direct marketing|/privacy_notice_direct_marketing|\\r\\n|4|Privacy notice (lightbox) - H&M online purchase|/privacy_notice_online_purchase|\\r\\n|5|Privacy notice (lightbox) – Customer service|/privacy_notice_customer_service|\\r\\n|6|Privacy notice (lightbox) – Cookie bar|/privacy_notice_cookies|\\r\\n\\r\\nh4. UX & COPY\\r\\nUX: https://hennesandmauritz.sharepoint.com/:p:/s/bznzimprovjoshua/EdAe6BegMg5ErzZA1LIZO_YBIxR6tVPD4bZ0bNeVzrCDaw?e=8pxZbV\\r\\nCopy: https://hennesandmauritz.sharepoint.com/:x:/s/bznzimprovjoshua/EZiV-5aRLUBFlXkYnVDSi0cBfDCj8iMbxsMB9kv-COmaHg?e=FQtcy7\\r\\n\\r\\nh4. Business contacts\\r\\n * Responsible BSA : Kristoffer Jalve\\r\\n\\r\\nh3. Acceptance criteria\\r\\nh5. Scenario 1: customer service overlay\\r\\n\\r\\nGIVEN tabletuser browsing on \\\"Customer Service – Contact\\\"\\r\\n WHEN user clicks on the privacy notice link \\r\\n THEN an overlay with the chapter regarding customer service will appear\\r\\nh5. Scenario 2: User click the link in the the privacy notice overlay\\r\\n\\r\\nGIVEN scenario 1\\r\\n WHEN user clicks on the privacy notice link in the bottom of the overylay\\r\\n THEN we´ll direct the user to a new page with the full privacy notice\",\"customfield_21380\":null,\"customfield_10252\":null,\"customfield_21379\":null,\"summary\":\"[OLIN-4583][Tablet] Display chapter Customer Service in the privacy notice on the Domain \\\"Customer Service – Contact\\\" \",\"customfield_21378\":null,\"customfield_21377\":null,\"customfield_21376\":null,\"customfield_21375\":null,\"customfield_11170\":null,\"customfield_15770\":null,\"customfield_21374\":null,\"customfield_21770\":null,\"customfield_21373\":null,\"customfield_21372\":null,\"customfield_21371\":null,\"customfield_11571\":\"2018-05-17T10:55:18.727+0200\",\"customfield_21370\":null,\"customfield_11572\":null,\"duedate\":null}},{\"expand\":\"operations,versionedRepresentations,editmeta,changelog,renderedFields\",\"id\":\"669443\",\"self\":\"https://jira.hm.com/rest/api/2/issue/669443\",\"key\":\"HMCOM-47513\",\"fields\":{\"customfield_16970\":\"2|i0jktb:\",\"customf